snippet.title: Warhammer Online Production Video Podcast # 12 - Music
snippet.description: This month we journey to the wonderfully gothic city of Prague in the Czech Republic to witness the aural wonders of the Prague Symphony Orchestra as they record the score for Warhammer Online. Sound Designer, Brad Derrick, shares his experience as the orchestra transforms a musical piece that he wrote on a keyboard in his car into a game soundtrack masterpiece.
